sub_title: Translator, teacher of the English language and Russian as a foreign language
summary:
EN <-> RU translator currently teaching  English to students of different languages and levels. I have been teaching for around 3 years so far, including online teaching, corporate training, groups and individual teaching. Highly motivated and open to opportunities and new experiences.
Volunteered as a translator during Judo (2014) and Taekwondo (2015) world championships.
